            consumer response. Many associate bright colors with better flavor,
            making it harder to give up.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; filter: blur(5px)">
            Synthetic food dyes, derived from petroleum-based chemicals, are
            widely used in the production of snacks and candies. Studies have
            linked them to
